File: AmaZulu King, Goodwill Zwelithini KaBhekuzulu. Rajesh Jantilal/AFP JOHANNESBURG - President Cyril Ramaphosa will deliver the eulogy at the memorial service of King Goodwill Zwelithini KaBhekuzulu. The monarch's memorial service will be held on Thursday. READ: Remembering King Zwelithini: Mourners pay their last respects The AmaZulu king will be planted on Wednesday night in a private ceremony. King Goodwill Zwelithini KaBhekuzulu passed away last week.